      section#dc-earning.col.s12
        h4 Earning Dragon Coins
        table.responsive-table.z-depth-1
          thead
            tr
              th Name
              th Location
              th Description
          tbody
            tr
              td
                label
                  input(type="checkbox")
                  span Daily Activity
              td Daily Button
              td You can earn 50 Dragon Coins each day for obtaining 120 Activeness each day. Push to 150 Activeness and you unlock a Pandora Heart/Seed set where you can gamble to get the S rank items or even obtain some enchanting materials which would normally cost you the Dragon coins to!
            tr
              td
                label
                  input(type="checkbox")
                  span Arena Chest Daily
              td Glory Shop
              td 50 Glory Points each for a box, there is a chance to obtain Dragon coins in them! Not to shabby for 3 boxes you can get for just completing your Arena Daily!
            tr
              td
                label
                  input(type="checkbox")
                  span Ladder Tournament
              td Arena
              td You gain 200 Glory as well as 20 Dragon coins on the first match each day, regardless if you win or lose! This also allows you to get all your Arena boxes if you hate PvP so you only need to do this once!
            tr
              td
                label
                  input(type="checkbox")
                  span Battle of Heroes Daily
              td Arena
              td You get 400 Glory and 50 Dragon Coins for winning the first Battle of Heroes! From what I know, you can also get the reward if you are the losing MVP, but more testing is required. Battle of Heroes also has a chance of earning Pandora Seeds too!
            tr
              td
                label
                  input(type="checkbox")
                  span Guild Red Envelopes/Red Envelopes
              td Guild
              td Being in a guild means you can get Red Envelopes each day for free from 20:00-22:00 server time! However, that is not all. Players can give red envelopes whenever they hit key milestones in the game. The bigger the guild, the more red envelopes there are, and of course the more Dragon coins you will naturally get! Of course, You can be Kale and always get 1 DC from each envelope, but let's be honest who is that unlucky?
            tr
              td
                label
                  input(type="checkbox")
                  span Achievements
              td Reward button
              td Don't underestimate the amount of Dragon coins gained by just earning achievements in the game. After every milestone you get rewards.
            tr
              td
                label
                  input(type="checkbox")
                  span Friend Gifting
              td Friend
              td After earning 12 friendliness each day, you are eligible to send a gift to your friend for free. Similarly, they can send you a gift too! You can only pick up three gifts a day, and you have a chance to get up to 20 dragon coins in the pack. Of course, there are other items in the box that are worth dragon coins so even though you didn't actually get the dragon coins it is still worth opening.
            tr
              td
                label
                  input(type="checkbox")
                  span Ladder Milestones
              td Arena
              td You get a sizable amount of dragon coins when attaining each rank. This resets once every three weeks when the ratings reset, so take full advantage and climb!
            tr
              td
                label
                  input(type="checkbox")
                  span Weekly Battle of Heroes
              td Arena
              td You can get an additional 100 Dragon Coins from Battle of Heroes after your 10th victory each week.
            tr
              td
                label
                  input(type="checkbox")
                  span Arena Nest
              td Arena
              td Clearing the Arena Nest for the first time nets you the Arena Nest Pack, containing 20 Green Agates, 100 Dragon Coins and 1 Forging Stone
            tr
              td
                label
                  input(type="checkbox")
                  span World Boss
              td World Boss #[br] (12:30-12:40 Server Time)
              td You get 20 dragon coins for participating in the world boss each day as long as you are in the top 5000 of players. While it is actually not plausible to not be top 5000, don't just press auto attack once and leave it! The higher you get the more guild contribution you get, which allows you to earn other things.
            tr
              td
                label
                  input(type="checkbox")
                  span Horse Racing
              td Daily Event #[br] (Mon/Wed 12:00)
              td Casual event for earning Dragon Coins! The higher you place, the more rewards you get.
            tr
              td
                label
                  input(type="checkbox")
                  span Riddle Party
              td Daily Event #[br] (Tue/Thur 12:00)
              td Casual event for earning Dragon Coins! You get 15 DC for every question you answered the fastest correctly.
            tr
              td
                label
                  input(type="checkbox")
                  span Weekend Party
              td Daily Event #[br] (Friday/Saturday/Sunday)
              td Casual event for earning Dragon Coins! You get 50 Dragon Coins on the first two runs you take. Win this for a Fairy Sweepstakes coupon!
            tr
              td
                label
                  input(type="checkbox")
                  span Guild Auction payout
              td Guild Auction
              td After every guild event, there will be a guild auction. Each guild member gets a portion of the proceeds when the auction is over, regardless if you have bidded on anything in the guild auction.
            tr
              td
                label
                  input(type="checkbox")
                  span Selling Cerberus items
              td Bazaar/Cerberus Nest
              td This is what I call spending money to earn more money! You can use 2 Cerberus Tickets (Obtainable for 30 DC) each day to obtain items to sell in the Bazaar! At best you can get the golden crate which gives you an unbound accessory piece to sell! At worst, you get a toothpick which still pretty much is bought for slightly above the cost you spent on the ticket. Note you should do this after you are working on the Manticore nest. Always use runs to benefit yourself before earning Dragon Coins.
            tr
              td
                label
                  input(type="checkbox")
                  span Bounty Run
              td Nest
              td Clear a bounty run (denoted "bounty" on the run itself) for a decent 5(?)-20 DC bonus. You get a nest bounty ticket every once in a while depending on your level.
            tr
              td
                label
                  input(type="checkbox")
                  span Banquet
              td Home
              td Complete Banquets for a sizable amount of dragon coins. This takes quite a bit of effort to complete, but I will assure that it is worth the effort. You can do up to 4 a week.
